### 搜索商户
GET http://{{host}}:{{port}}/merchants/search?name=&status=&page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json;charset=UTF-8

### 获取所有启用的商户
GET http://{{host}}:{{port}}/merchants
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json;charset=UTF-8

### 获取商户
GET http://{{host}}:{{port}}/merchants/1
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json;charset=UTF-8

### 添加商户
POST http://{{host}}:{{port}}/merchants
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json;charset=UTF-8

{
  "account": "colin",
  "name": "代码小店",
  "password": "123456",
  "scope": "承接各种疑难代码",
  "shopName": "代码小店"
}

### 编辑商户
PUT http://{{host}}:{{port}}/merchants/1541326285035409408
Accept: application/json
