### 删除商户
DELETE http://{{host}}:{{port}}/merchants/2
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json;charset=UTF-8

### 启用商户
PUT http://{{host}}:{{port}}/merchants/1541326285035409408/enable
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json;charset=UTF-8

### 禁用商户
PUT http://{{host}}:{{port}}/merchants/1541326285035409408/disable
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json;charset=UTF-8

